5. Lateral Movement Behavior
Baseline normal remote administration patterns.

Protocols to monitor:

Port	Use
3389	RDP
445	SMB
5985	WinRM
135	RPC
Baseline example:

Admin-PC → Servers (RDP)
Backup Server → All hosts (SMB)
Anomalies:

Workstation → Workstation SMB

User workstation performing RDP to many machines

